  "abilities": {
    "core": [
      "Deep Strike Precision Drop: In your Movement phase , when this unit is set up on the battlefield using the Deep Strike ability, it can perform a precision drop. If it does, this unit can be set up anywhere on the battlefield that is more than 6\" horizontally away from all enemy units, but until the end of the turn, it is not eligible to declare a charge . Servo-sentry: When this unit is set up on the battlefield using the Deep Strike ability, the Tempestor Aquilon can shoot with its sentry weapon (its sentry flamer, sentry grenade launcher or sentry hot-shot volley gun)."
